						<div class="postbody">The OP was talking about inserting a MIDI file into a SPC file with hex editor, that's imply that full GM set is there. And actually no, a sample manager would be more complex than just a simple scanner, as you have to dynamically allocate all needed samples in memory and tell player where they are. For MIDI you would expect to have multilayer instruments, that'll add extra complexity. Not to say it is something very complex, but I think it'll be more complex than a simple custom format music player.</div>

